	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">如果你喜欢那些与自然融为一体的房子，别错过这本书</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-16 12:47:46 +0800"></span>
